498
00:33:57,600 --> 00:34:01,800
♫ もう二度と戻らない ♫

499
00:34:01,800 --> 00:34:04,200
♫ God, help me do it, all right ♫

500
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:08,200
♫ God, help me do it, all right ♫

